text: Garima Vikrant Singh (Garima Srivastav) is an Indian actress best known for her role as Saraswati in Life OK's Gustakh Dil. She appeared in shows like, Choti Bahu Season 2, (Zee TV), Phir Subah Hogi (Zee TV), Rahe Tera Aasheervad (Colors), Chand ke paar Chalo (Imagine) and Parivaar (Zee TV). == References == == Other websites == * * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Indian television actors
